{"tid":92687,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"虐待動物？老鼠遭便利店員五花大綁「批鬥」","createTime":"2017-01-23T18:51:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-24T04:59:06.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"af8fbe750df3d16954e3db5b4274b2f525daddea","tid":92687,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T18:51:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170123/photo/bkncn-20170123130043754-0123_05011_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170123%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170123130043754-0123_05011_001_01p.jpg&h=ddc52561&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n老鼠遭人五花大綁「批鬥」。（網上圖片） <br />\n<br />\n老鼠是商戶的「大敵」，不但帶來衞生問題，更會咬爛及偷吃貨物。有廣東網民在微博上貼文，指其任職便利店員的朋友在倉庫發現到一隻小老鼠，為了懲罰該隻老鼠，其朋友將老鼠五花大綁，並在其身上掛上「悔過書」，如「批鬥」一樣，但未有交代老鼠下場。有網民笑言：「笑死」，但也有網民認為「至於（這樣做）嗎？太殘忍了」。 <br />\n<br />\n從照片所見，老鼠「大字型」被半空懸吊在手推車的旁邊，其身上被人掛上寫有「呵，小子就這點能耐嗎？就算把我打死，我也不會承認你家的大米是我偷的」及「我在（再）也不敢了」的字牌。有人則在老鼠面前舉機拍照。 <br />\n<br />\n涉事人員懲罰老鼠的手法在網上引來熱議，有人看到照片後稱：「笑到不行了」、「鼠竊狗偷，不值同情」、「求老鼠心理陰影面積」，連深圳交警官微也發出三個掩嘴笑的表情符號作回應；但有人則認為處理手法太過分：「人類比老鼠更可怕」、「醉了，殘忍」、「虐待動物！」；有人更代入老鼠：「士可殺不可辱！」、「你們人類就是戲多!」 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170123/bkncn-20170123130043754-0123_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170123%2Fbkncn-20170123130043754-0123_05011_001.html&d=uFkZx1s7nkArXKMgcnoP%2BqEBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=2d2b06c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170123/bkncn-20170123130043754-0123_05011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"77ff02297a77ac579aaa643928ee4e2e8f325188","tid":92687,"uid":43398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T19:00:53.000Z","msg":"話唔定係想俾其他老鼠見到嚇下佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋相比起黐鼠膠、用捕鼠夾、用籠活捉之後再淋滾水甚至直接掟落街，五花大綁都算係咁㗎喇"},{"pid":"6a95df0e55c9f0523ab1b37d091849fdc7a38f0a","tid":92687,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T19:02:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f15683f92271d0ad4af53b9baf16fc2ebab4e4da","tid":92687,"uid":27731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T19:03:45.000Z","msg":"我係咪有病 我覺得隻野幾可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f86afd19623cfab6af910433e2291e609d15442","tid":92687,"uid":17569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T19:06:15.000Z","msg":"On9當有趣"},{"pid":"e46edd159adb845470a56bf98dfc35ef90abc915","tid":92687,"uid":18955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T19:07:21.000Z","msg":"樓主坐左幾多碌？"},{"pid":"83d304828f647682f8ea212bb20daf47b3d73130","tid":92687,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T04:59:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}